headline: State Street to Speak at the BofA Securities Financial Services Conference
summary: BOSTON, January 29, 2026--State Street Corporation (NYSE: STT) announced today that its Chief Financial Officer, John Woods, will present at the BofA Securities Financial Services Conference in Miami, FL on Tuesday, February 10, 2026 at approximately 1:50 pm ET.
